## Report Types

### Summary Report
- Executive overview
- Pass/fail statistics
- Critical issues only
- Key recommendations

### Full Report
- All test results
- Every bug with details
- All screenshots
- Complete analysis

### Bugs-Only Report
- Bug list
- Reproducible steps
